name: Tricky Trap
description:
Enjoy over 50 levels of complex mazes and most difficult levels in this Tricky Trap

Are you sound enough to escape the complex traps within the game?

It’s time to battle the timer and dive deep into solving a huge mind bent puzzle trap! There is no limitation to your moves.

Use your finger to drive the ball through the frustrating passages to survive spitting the distance.

Can you really get out of this trap?
